1. Product North Star & MVP Philosophy
1.1 The One Thing That Matters
 A farmer must be able to log today's feed in under 10 seconds. Everything else is secondary.
AquaRythu exists for one reason: shrimp farmers in Andhra Pradesh and Telangana lose 20–30% of
potential profit because of poor feed discipline. They either overfeed (high FCR, wasted cost) or
underfeed (stunted growth, missed harvest window). Both problems are solvable with data — if the app
is fast enough for farmers to actually use it.
