4. Complete Data Layer — Supabase Schema
4.1 Schema Overview
Run supabase/schema.sql in Mumbai region (ap-south-1) project. Enable RLS on all tables. Enable
Realtime on feed_logs.
Table Rows per Farmer/Crop Key Purpose
users 1 per farmer Auth + subscription
farms 1–3 per farmer Farm details
ponds 1–6 per farm Pond config
stockings 1 per crop per pond Crop lifecycle
feed_plans 30× per stocking (blind) Reference feed schedule
feed_logs 4–6× per day per pond
(×90+ days) Core operational data
tray_checks 4× per feed_log (post DOC
15) Tray status + multiplier
sampling 1 per 10 days per pond ABW + biomass
water_log ~3× per week per pond Water quality
supplements 2–5 per crop per pond Supplement plans
supplement_logs Per application Actual supplement given
harvests 1–5 per crop Revenue tracking
mortality_log Daily if needed Survival tracking
alerts Generated, dismissed daily Alert history
