6.2 Write Flow
48.User taps MARK AS FED
49.App immediately adds entry to SharedPreferences queue (optimistic)
50.UI shows DONE immediately (don't wait for network)
51.In background: attempt Supabase INSERT
52.On success: remove from queue
53.On failure (network): leave in queue; retry on next connectivity event
6.3 Sync Flow
54.connectivity_plus streams online/offline events
55.On connectivity restored: read full queue
56.Process queue in FIFO order
57.For each item: INSERT/UPDATE to Supabase
58.On success: remove from queue
59.On repeated failure (>5 retries): mark as 'failed'; show banner to user
 Queue-able operations: feed_logs, tray_checks, sampling, water_log, mortality_log, harvests
